network.param.modules.receipts

Interface IReceiptManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBulkImport, IReceiptBulkImport
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReceiptManager

    public interface IReceiptManager
extends IReceiptBulkImport
    IReceiptManager is an implementation of core param protocol, using this interface user can able to post receipt into ParamNetwork.
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
